OL,5, A journalist for the Polish state      
OL,6, broadcaster has apologised for his     
OL,7, channel's "shameful" role in spreading 
OL,8, anti-LGBT sentiment.                   
OL,10,FHost Wojciech Szelag said that LGBT    
OL,11,Fpeople had been targeted for "years" by
OL,12,F"hateful words".                       
OL,14,FThe channel, TVP Info, was criticised  
OL,15,Fas a mouthpiece of the previous        
OL,16,Fgoverning Law and Justice (PiS) party. 
OL,18,FBut pro-EU Prime Minister Donald Tusk, 
OL,19,Fwho came to power in December, has     
OL,20,Foverseen changes to the broadcaster.   
